{
  "stem": "19441.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 501.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you crazy?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you always said such a crazy idea, now we have to do that anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that Polish woman-- [INAUDIBLE], her name I remember-- she was a terrible, sadistic woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She stirred up the woman commanders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What, is she going to-- you are going to listen to what the man says?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You are in charge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they-- then they sent me from punishment to the new experimental barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[POINTING] Block 10 was a men's camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my life went from here to there, from there to here, from here to there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never a dull moment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The experimental barrack, they-- some German doctors, they wanted to save themselves from Siberia and to the front, so they used their doctor knowledge.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted to make experiments on human which, which was-- didn't cost them anything, and they said that for the good of the German nation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they established there a-- a barrack which was the only woman barrack in the men's camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- the windows was woodened up so we shouldn't have contact.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and there they did the experiments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And way I, I told you yesterday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I arrived there, because I had very blonde hair-- and being in the rain and, and-- in the rain and in the sunshine, so my hair was very bleached-- I looked really very blonde.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was skinny, so it-- I looked taller than I am, and also my bones shriveled through arthritis, by the way.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, you can't be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is a mistake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I am Jewish, like all others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't be.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why do you think I can't be?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I think that we must be mistake.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
